      "x": 80,
      "y": 598,
      "width": 350,
      "height": 176,
      "text": "DATACLASS: AuditRecord: A single\nauditable operation.\n\nMETHODS:\n+ to_dict(): Serialize to a dict\nfor SQL insertion or JSON output.",
