      "id": "cls1-desc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 630,
      "y": 492,
      "width": 970,
      "height": 254,
      "text": "CLASS: AuditLogger: Collects audit records and flushes them to a pluggable backend.\n\nMETHODS:\n+ log(operation, role_name, workspace_id, item_id, success, source_file, content_hash, error):\nRecord an operation.\n\n+ flush(): Send all accumulated records to the writer, then clear the buffer.\n\n+ to_dicts(): Serialize all records for inspection or manual persistence.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CLASS: AuditLogger: Collects audit records and flushes them to a pluggable backend.\n\nMETHODS:\n+ log(operation, role_name, workspace_id, item_id, success, source_file, content_hash, error):\nRecord an operation.\n\n+ flush(): Send all accumulated records to the writer, then clear the buffer.\n\n+ to_dicts(): Serialize all records for inspection or manual persistence.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 18
    },
